Requirements
============
- python 2.4+
- python-setuptools 0.6c7+
- buildbot 0.7.5
- Linux/Unix

Installation
============
Use the rpm ... or 
- Become root (or root like) user
- run python setup.py install
- verify it installed with python -c "import loki"
  No traceback means it's good!
  
RPM
===
To create an rpm ...
- Edit loki.spec
- python setup.py sdist
- rpmbuild -ba loki.spec
